      // googleon: all

    .footer
      :markdown-it
        Created by [Paul Nechifor](/). [View the Git source.](https://github.com/paul-nechifor/pseudoromanian)

      small: :markdown-it
        [Home](/) •
        [Blog](/blog) •
        [Projects](/projects) •
        [Twitter](https://twitter.com/PaulNechifor)

    script !{js}
